thread.title: Anti-racism marchers converge in Washington on MLK anniversary

title: Anti-racism marchers converge in Washington on MLK anniversary
text:
Anti-racism marchers converge in Washington on MLK anniversary 3:30am IST - 00:35 
People gathered in Washington, D.C. on Wednesday to attend the ACT to End Racism Rally, which coincides with the 50th anniversary of the assassination of civil rights leader Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
